# AI Agent Rules

## Purpose
AI calls per `docs/AI_AGENT_SPEC.md` and BR-AI*.

## Requirements
- Outbound requires consent_recorded or inquiry opt-in BR-AI01.
- DND registry check before dial BR-AI05.
- Recording disclosure in call script.
- Whisper transcription + GPT extraction jobs async.
- Apply inquiry auto-fill only if confidence >= 0.8 BR-AI04.
- Deduct AI minutes on connect; track in organization_usage.
- Store recordings S3 KMS encrypted.

## Restrictions
- No OpenAI keys in frontend.
- Telecaller cannot export bulk transcripts without permission.
- No outbound to numbers on org DND block list.

## Best Practices
- Lead score 0-100 persisted on call + sync to inquiry.
- Retry transcription 3x then alert ops.
- Quota check before initiating call.

## Anti-Patterns
- Synchronous wait for transcript in API request.
- Auto-updating inquiry with low-confidence hallucinated budget.

## Examples

```typescript
await this.complianceService.assertCanDial(dto.clientPhone, ctx);
await this.quotaService.assertAiMinutesAvailable(ctx.tenantId);
return this.callQueue.add('initiate_call', { ...dto, tenantId: ctx.tenantId });
```
